## 第三阶段：分三个会话执行（核心）

> 云端模式下不要用一个超长会话跑完全部——拆成3个会话，每个会话产出一个PR，
> 你在iPad上审一眼、点合并，再开下一个。失败重跑的代价也小。

### 第7步：会话A — 数据层 + 对话核心（Phase 0-2）

新建云端会话，选 `pulsecity` 仓库 + `pulsecity-env` 环境，粘贴：

```
Read PulseCity_VibeCoding_Guide_v2.md fully before starting.

MISSION: Implement Phases 0-2 of the PulseCity build (scaffold, types,
mock data, city tools, chat API with tool use + SSE streaming).

CLOUD-SPECIFIC RULES:
1. This repo already contains md files and a .gitignore — initialize
   Next.js 14 IN PLACE around them (move conflicting files temporarily
   if create-next-app refuses, then restore).
2. Do NOT create .env.local — environment variables are provided by the
   cloud environment. Code must read process.env directly. DO create
   .env.example documenting the 4 required keys.
3. Create CLAUDE.md at repo root exactly as specified in guide section 1
   and COMMIT it — future sessions depend on it.
4. Never ask me questions. Ambiguous calls → choose simpler, log in
   DECISIONS.md.

TASKS (from the guide):
- Guide Prompt 1: scaffold + deps (mapbox-gl, react-map-gl, swr, zustand,
  date-fns, lucide-react, @anthropic-ai/sdk)
- Guide Prompt 2: lib/types.ts + lib/mock-data.ts
- Guide Prompt 3: lib/city-tools.ts (4 tools: search_events, query_poi,
  get_predictions, get_area_status)
- Guide Prompt 4: app/api/chat/route.ts (claude-sonnet-4-6, agentic tool
  loop capped at 5 iterations, SSE streaming) + lib/chat-client.ts

ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA (all must pass before you finish):
AC-1: npm run build exits 0
AC-2: npx tsc --noEmit exits 0; zero `: any` in lib/types.ts
AC-3: SEATTLE_POIS has 30 entries, SEATTLE_EVENTS has 12 (3 predicted);
      all coords within lat 47.5-47.75, lng -122.45 to -122.2
      (write a node assertion script, run it, keep it in scripts/)
AC-4: write scripts/test-chat.mjs — start `npm run dev` in background,
      POST a chat message about Capitol Hill to /api/chat, parse SSE:
      assert >=1 tool_call event, >=1 text_delta event, exactly 1 done
      event, 0 error events. Then test "Find me dinner not near any
      events" — assert referencedPois is non-empty. Kill dev server after.
AC-5: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY referenced only in server-side files
      (grep check: never in any 'use client' file)

ON FAILURE: 3 fix attempts per criterion, then apply guide fallback
rules, log in DECISIONS.md, continue.

DELIVERABLE: commit everything including PROGRESS.md (one status line
per phase) and DECISIONS.md. Push and create a PR titled
"Phase 0-2: Data layer + conversational core". PR description must
include: test results from scripts/test-chat.mjs, all decisions made,
any fallbacks triggered.
```

发出去后你就可以放下iPad了。会话在云端持续运行，随时打开App看实时进度，还能中途发消息纠偏。

**完成后**：GitHub App会通知你有新PR。打开PR → 看描述里的测试结果 → 没问题就点 **Merge pull request**。

### 第8步：会话B — UI + 三屏联动（Phase 3-4）

合并PR A之后，新建会话（同仓库同环境），粘贴：

```
Read CLAUDE.md and PulseCity_VibeCoding_Guide_v2.md fully. Phases 0-2
are complete and merged — verify by running npm install && npm run build
first. If build fails on main, fix it before proceeding.

MISSION: Implement Phases 3-4 (all UI components + integration).

TASKS:
- Build the UI yourself following the design specs in guide section 2
  (skip all v0.dev references): MapView, EventFeed, ChatPanel,
  EventDetailDrawer, ToolCallIndicator, PredictionCard
- Guide Prompt 6: app/api/events/route.ts + lib/geo-utils.ts
- Guide Prompt 7: lib/prediction-engine.ts
- Guide section 4.1 wiring: 60/40 split layout, map markers with pulsing
  rings, chat streaming UI with tool-call indicator, POI chips in chat
  that highlight + flyTo on the map, selectedEvent → impact radius +
  detail drawer

ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA:
AC-1: npm run build exits 0
AC-2: curl /api/events returns >=12 events with distanceMiles when
      lat/lng provided
AC-3: extend scripts/test-chat.mjs — referencedPois entries must have
      lat/lng matching entries in SEATTLE_POIS
AC-4: predicted events render dashed border + PREDICTED badge (grep)
AC-5: the prop chain chat→page→map highlightedPois exists and the
      event chain feed→page→drawer+map exists (verify by reading
      page.tsx, document both chains in PROGRESS.md)
AC-6: dev server runs 60s with 3 chat queries fired, zero unhandled
      errors

NEVER ask questions. Same fallback policy as before (guide rules).
Mapbox heatmap layer issues → ship markers-only, log it.

DELIVERABLE: update PROGRESS.md + DECISIONS.md, push, PR titled
"Phase 3-4: UI and integration" with screenshots if possible
(describe the rendered layout in the PR body regardless).
```

### 第9步：会话C — 数据增强 + 打磨（Phase 5-7）

合并PR B之后，最后一个会话：

```
Read CLAUDE.md and PulseCity_VibeCoding_Guide_v2.md. Phases 0-4 merged.
Verify npm run build passes on main first.

MISSION: Phases 5-7 (Reddit + Haiku classification, polish, final report).

TASKS:
- Guide Prompt 5: reddit-client.ts + classify-events.ts
  (claude-haiku-4-5, ONE batched call per fetch) + /api/reddit route.
  If REDDIT_CLIENT_ID env var is empty: implement the module but
  hard-wire mock-only mode, log it.
- Animations: pulse-ring, fade-in-up, typing-dot keyframes; drawer
  slide transition; staggered map bubble entrance
- Realtime simulation hooks: useRealtimeEvents, useCityPulse,
  useBreakingAlert (guide v1 Prompt 13 spec, referenced in v2 §4.3)
- Responsive: desktop-first; tablet/mobile per guide §4.2 — this is
  the FIRST thing to cut if struggling
- vercel.json: maxDuration 60 for /api/chat, CORS headers
- README.md: env vars table + deploy steps

ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA:
AC-1: clean build (rm -rf .next first) exits 0
AC-2: /api/reddit responds within 5s and ALWAYS includes the 12 mock
      events (fault-injection test: invalid creds → graceful fallback)
AC-3: keyframes present in CSS (grep pulse-ring, fade-in-up, typing-dot)
AC-4: useRealtimeEvents consumed in page.tsx
AC-5: FINAL_REPORT.md exists with: per-phase summary, top decisions,
      KNOWN_ISSUES, "needs human attention" list (visual polish items),
      and exact local-run + Vercel deploy instructions

DELIVERABLE: push, PR titled "Phase 5-7: Live data + polish + report".
Include FINAL_REPORT.md content in the PR description.
```

